so accomplished\nrecently by Allen, Clausen and Isenberg, although their result is restricted to\nthe near-CMC case and to smoother background metrics and data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Dec 2007 19:27:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 31 Mar 2008 10:52:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 3 Apr 2008 09:19:26 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 12 Apr 2008 07:45:04 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 29 Aug 2008 05:37:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-01-13"}
