 exchange in AdS, yields a universal prediction for CFT's with AdS\ngravitational duals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Dec 2007 19:23:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 Feb 2008 09:43:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-02-06"}
